            </description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">好奇的阿哲</dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 02 Mar 2022 15:13:37 +0800</pubDate><guid>http://www.zhihu.com/question/322879658/answer/2325189909</guid></item><item><title>动漫摇曳露营中有哪些现实中存在的露营器材？</title><link>http://www.zhihu.com/question/266747396/answer/2326389973?utm_campaign=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_source=rss&amp;utm_content=title</link><description>&lt;p data-pid="y8TlXNIq"&gt;《摇曳露营△》中的露营装备，都是现实中存在的，前几天刚好重温了一遍，就顺便把里面出现的装备整理一番。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Mont-bell Moonlight Tent 3 型&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-pid="bjwSH7uz"&gt;链接：&lt;a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B07YRJRGKS%3Ftag%3Dnomad-base-22%26linkCode%3Dogi%26th%3D1%26psc%3D1" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;mont-bell ムーンライトテント3型&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;备注：经典的A字帐篷，已停产&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-62de6ba010065b6587096fad98042325_720w.jpg?rss" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="700" data-rawheight="385" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-62de6ba010065b6587096fad98042325" data-watermark-src="v2-207024c49eeaf90c5bd2d372c0941fd0" data-private-watermark-src="v2-d1f40eb8cdd4aafacc83ab8a73cf913e" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-62fff2952d22ad8793fef280a3778ace_720w.jpg?rss" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="700" data-rawheight="453" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-62fff2952d22ad8793fef280a3778ace" data-watermark-src="v2-82bcade2ebda94f8df8af5f820cf5bb6" data-private-watermark-src="v2-4fb249fc164fcce0ade9ee60eb35a21c" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ac2c5be9f6be05844124ca43560c2653_720w.jpg?rss" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="888" data-rawheight="676" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-ac2c5be9f6be05844124ca43560c2653" data-watermark-src="v2-ca2afeae4179d1f9abe91720